@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000
@json = application/json

### Healthcheck básico (frontend)
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### Dashboard (default)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard

### Dashboard (límites personalizados)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard?history_limit=50&snapshots_limit=200

### Historial paginado
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/history?limit=20&offset=0&range_name=all

### Historial paginado (7 días)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/history?limit=20&offset=20&range_name=7d

### Snapshots paginados
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/snapshots?limit=20&offset=0

### Métricas backend
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/metrics

### Compactar historial manualmente
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/history/compact

### Guardar registro manual
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/manual-record
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "market_silver": 365900000000,
  "inventory_silver": 1200000000,
  "preorder_silver": 7600000000
}

### Captura OCR almacén
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ocr/storage
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "warehouse": "Heidel",
  "market_silver": 5400000000
}

### Corrección manual por almacén
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/manual-warehouse-value
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "warehouse": "Heidel",
  "market_silver": 5500000000
}

### Captura OCR inventario
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ocr/inventory
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "inventory_silver": 1300000000
}

### Ingresar preorder
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/preorders
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "preorder_silver": 7800000000,
  "source": "browser-extension",
  "details": {
    "region": "NA",
    "note": "test .http"
  }
}

### Settings: incluir almacenes en total (ON)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/settings/include-warehouses/1

### Settings: incluir almacenes en total (OFF)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/settings/include-warehouses/0

### Info endpoint de WebSocket
GET {{baseUrl}}/ws/updates

### WebSocket updates (si tu cliente HTTP lo soporta)
# WEBSOCKET ws://127.0.0.1:8000/ws/updates
# Si abre conexión, puedes enviar un ping de texto:
# ping
